snippet.title: UNCURSED - TRAILER ( NEW HORROR GAME )
snippet.description:
About Uncursed Game : 
Step into the chilling world of Grandma's House of Horrors, a heart-pounding horror game that will test your courage and nerve. After a 3 months of unanswered calls, Alex returns to his grandmother's house, only to discover a seemingly peaceful scene. However, a sudden turn of events shatters the tranquility.

Wishlist it on Steam : 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3316910/UNCURSED/
